Download only audio w/o video
  https://askubuntu.com/questions/423508/can-i-directly-download-audio-using-youtube-dl

Specify size to fetch
  $ youtube-dl -f 'bestvideo[height<=240]+bestaudio/best[height<=240]' ...

Re-encode .wav audio
  CBR: $ youtube-dl -x --audio-format mp3 --audio-quality 196K -- ...
  VBR: $ youtube-dl -x --audio-format mp3 --audio-quality 7 -- ...

